00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:29.120
Ayo kembali!  Ayo!

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:33.000
Ayo!  - Guddan!

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:34.600
Akshat...
- AJ!

00:09:34.760 --> 00:09:36.320
Ayo!  - Akshat!

00:09:48.800 --> 00:09:50.320
AJ!  - Guddan.

