00:15:25.320 --> 00:15:27.240
Dia adalah wanita yang
licik dan manipulatif.

00:15:27.400 --> 00:15:29.160
Saraswati Jindal, alias Saru!

00:15:29.720 --> 00:15:30.880
Menantu perempuan bungsu!

00:15:31.000 --> 00:15:32.560
Pak, dia memaksaku.

00:15:32.680 --> 00:15:34.880
