00:15:40.640 --> 00:15:41.800
Pak, dialah orangnya.

00:15:49.680 --> 00:15:51.720
Hei kau!  Bodoh!

00:15:51.960 --> 00:15:53.480
Saya telah menelepon

00:15:53.800 --> 00:15:56.640
polisi palsu ini dari
perusahaan drama.

00:15:58.360 --> 00:15:59.280
Dipahami?

